com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns.activities
Class EmailActivityType

java.lang.Object
  com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns.activities.EmailActivityType

public final class EmailActivityType
extends Object

Class to store possible values for Email Activity Type for the Email Campaigns Service in Constant Contact.
These are read-only values and are returned by the tracking APIs.
A value from this class should be present where an activityType field is needed.

Author:
ConstantContact
